/static/inside-index-html-inline-styling.0f2f19f.985fd0fa91b6af893bda9305fe6bc7bf.png 1353w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" data-src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/inside-index-html-inline-styling.0f2f19f.985fd0fa91b6af893bda9305fe6bc7bf.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/inside-index-html-inline-styling.0f2f19f.985fd0fa91b6af893bda9305fe6bc7bf.png\" width=\"1353\" alt=\"inline styling HTML content\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Coba buka pada browser, maka akan menghasilkan tampilan Heading Text yang berwarna biru. Seperti di bawah ini: </p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 621 178' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-142b40ec84de798b08f4b140f3e47394'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-142b40ec84de798b08f4b140f3e47394)' width='621' height='178' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAASCAYAAADrL9giAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAEyUlEQVRYw%2b1X%2b09URxTmX2t/7m9NW9s0sZY0sdZG24aqtQVjxQryEiiIzxQUC7gLGC0gyKuALSLsylMXeT%2bssO/HXZa99%2bs3d3bh7u5FiYWkDZ1kMnNnzvnOnO%2bcObObZrfbsZdbms1m0yfr6yo0TYOqavoYnxu//0nfFpaJzHbtR6MavUi0sx3dDQIAVQcQjet6jzfjd/J6ckuWFT0aNd/XraqpWGItGft13zKIm/O4zfhoJq9nwJMnNqhULClV0der4fLVzc3628DMosFANPXgRoNbESLaoz7gbkvSXmyMRORoewTcadrcD/qAGzeIHRPs/wOYnkvEiMSctvKsHR1AJ/v9VuD5FNBCrIHHgNO1NQlpdrvMgI8%2bVFFQoOGrDODh70BFBXA%2bB8i7AFwsB54%2blwqT40B%2bEWAf4l4%2b8Gs1cOUa958CheeB9h4eeI17uZx3cu8y0NAAZH5HPOrV1QBVN4n5M5BDmcZGIDubuLMkiXY/%2bRSooTO3iFtF508cp3NWaaOykk7dB8pLgWaOp0%2bRtDGgpw347LA83yzPue99oLYeKM7j%2bufAiss8aJIAZoDI/vR0FXV1Gr4hAWV0%2br0PeLAzwEECHz9GpwuYDfOA%2byWwfz8zpgR4623JehYPMjAAvPsOnSyRwF8fAQ7QmeyzwIVC4PCXwDk6fIR4B78AfiAhhzjmkrQM4ntDjDAJyPiWeFnUPcAMJDknScDJE7SZDhTxXOVlwMf76Hy2lBVtgnX8EPFdHp5xBmhl