>color</code></h5>\n<p>salah satu <strong>property</strong> yang ada di CSS. Fungsinya untuk memberi warna pada text.</p>\n<h5 id=\"blue\"><a href=\"#blue\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code>blue</code></h5>\n<p>value dari property <code>color</code>. property <code>color</code> menerima value warna yang berupa text ataupun hex code. misal: <code>#000000</code>. </p>\n<p>Gimana udah mulai bingung? gapapa... namanya juga belajar, pelan-pelan pemahannnya akan bertambah. Semangat terus yak.</p>\n<h2 id=\"style-tag\"><a href=\"#style-tag\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Style Tag</h2>\n<p>Selain melakukan styling secara langsung pada tag HTML, kita juga bisa menggunakan tag <code>&#x3C;style></code>. apa dan gimana sih tag <code>&#x3C;style></code> itu? yuk kita coba praktikkan.</p>\n<p>Pada HTML yang telah kita buat sebelumnya, terdapat tag <code>&#x3C;head></code> coba tambahkan tag <code>&#x3C;style></code> di dalam tag <code>&#x3C;head></code> tersebut. Seperti ini:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- file location: belajar-santuy/index.html --></span>\n\n...\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Belajar CSS santuy<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n      <span class=\"token selector\">b</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token hexcode color\">#6E75A8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">white</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n...</code></pre>\n<p>Tampilan ketika di browser</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 596 178' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-15e8e1a9ba31752901ef2f024db6c7bd'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-15e8e1a9ba31752901ef2f024db6c7bd)' width='596' height='178' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAATCAYAAAAgcwuHAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAFYUlEQVRYw%2bVY6VNTVxTP39UP/QMcZ/rNMtMZ12mnm/YLY%2btSatUqaClQcAEHEC0EgUBYFLIQlrAkQAJBk6IIoSCGRcuSlArJe7/%2bXu57eY%2bAyojtTIc3c%2bbee%2b7Z7u%2bee07A5PP5EI/HEYvFsLa2tufIFAgEoHyyjD35mUZGRpKTREIiCDIkSU6OGqWvd0s7sbedzE7jSCSUmxTyCilzjbedfAoAQFIVOJMEaZ8yVzJEyxLjWiNJ3srbtJ/Yai99NPoQl/L6ONLJ%2bL16pc/X11VbcV3OKG8aCQgAsrMl%2bP0ysnMorAoM9gLNtq0BvOs3/gi4XfkWIfoovgH8GdNZPi9g